Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 leechcraft-anhero (= ${binary:Version}),
 leechcraft-eiskaltdcpp (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Extra LeechCraft plugins beyond full installation
 This metapackage installs additional LeechCraft plugins that may
 pull a lot of dependencies on some systems (like AnHero pulling
 half of KDE).
