 leechcraft-sidebar
Description: UPower-based power manager for LeechCraft
 This package contains Liznoo, UPower-based power manager. Liznoo also detects
 suspend/resume events and allows other plugins to respond correspondingly.
 For example Azoth gracefully disconnects from the servers after receiving
 suspend notification, and reconnects back after resume.
