Package: leechcraft-newlife
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends},
 libleechcraft-xmlsettingsdialog0.3.0 (= ${binary:Version}),
 libleechcraft-util0.5.0 (= ${binary:Version}),
 leechcraft (= ${binary:Version})
Provides: leechcraft-provider-importer
Description: Settings importer for LeechCraft
 This package contains importer of settings, preferences etc. from
 various applications into LeechCraft. Currently it supports importing
 RSS feeds and settings from Akregator and Liferea.
 .
 LeechCraft is a free modular "Internet client" application.
 .
 LeechCraft allows one to browse the web, read RSS/Atom feeds, download
 files via BitTorrent, HTTP, FTP and Direct Connect, automatically stream,
 download or play podcasts and other media files and much more.

