 libleechcraft-util0.5.0 (= ${binary:Version}),
 leechcraft (= ${binary:Version})
Provides: leechcraft-provider-securestorage
Description: Security Manager plugin for LeechCraft
 This package contains the base plugin for secure storage stuff for LeechCraft
 and its own sub-plugin:
  * simplestorage (Simple storage backend)
  This is a simple, unencrypted storage backend for  SecMan, LeechCraft's
  security manager plugin.
