Package: leechcraft-sidebar
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends},
 libleechcraft-xmlsettingsdialog0.3.0 (= ${binary:Version}),
 libleechcraft-util0.5.0 (= ${binary:Version}),
 leechcraft (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Sidebar with quick launch, tabs and tray areas in LeechCraft
 This package contains module that adds a nice sidebar with quick launch area,
 tabs and tray-like area. The sidebar supports grouping of similar tabs (like
 browser tabs or tabs from one web site), and it also supports hiding unneeded
 launch actions and tray items.
