Provides: leechcraft-provider-sessionmanager
Description: Tab Session Manager for LeechCraft
 This plugin stores the list and state of opened tabs between LeechCraft runs.
 It supports different types of tabs, like browser tab, IM chat or else.
 It also supports manually saving and restoring different sessions.
